### Order Management API — sample requests
### Use with the VS Code "REST Client" extension or the JetBrains/VS HTTP client.

@host = http://localhost:5216

### Health check
GET {{host}}/api/health
Accept: application/json

### Run document synchronisation
# First run against the seeded orders returns created 6 / skipped 1 (ORD-999 has no order).
POST {{host}}/api/sync/documents
Accept: application/json

### Get documents for a seeded order
GET {{host}}/api/orders/ORD-001/documents
Accept: application/json

### Get documents for an unknown order -> 404 ProblemDetails
GET {{host}}/api/orders/ORD-404/documents
Accept: application/json

### Synchronisation history (newest first), default paging
GET {{host}}/api/sync/logs
Accept: application/json

### Synchronisation history with paging
GET {{host}}/api/sync/logs?page=1&pageSize=10
Accept: application/json

### Invalid paging -> 400 validation ProblemDetails
GET {{host}}/api/sync/logs?page=0&pageSize=500
Accept: application/json

### OpenAPI document
GET {{host}}/swagger/v1/swagger.json
Accept: application/json


